title: Follow live updates from Week 8 of high school football
text:
Easton's football team will attempt to return to winning ways against Liberty on Friday. (lehighvalleylive.com file photo) By lehighvalleylive sports staff View/Post Comments 
Week 8's impressive slate of high school football action might be difficult to keep track of, but lehighvalleylive is here to help. 
Follow updates from reporters and athletic departments in the comments section at the bottom of this post to stay informed on games from across the region.
